You are entitled to your own religious beliefs, but you are NOT entitled to spread hate and dehumanize people because of said beliefs.

We do not support hate. It's not about opinions.
You are talking about human lives.
We've come so far in terms of diversity and individuality, let's not go back in time.

No one should approve or validate someone based on their sexual identity.
